descriptionHtml:

"A good life comes through a good habit."

If you become a good person every day with good habits,
you will gain a good life.
Let's start a good habit from DotHabit!

DotHabit makes daily habits visible with dots.
You will get a sense of achievement and you will be encouraged to continue.

Features of DotHabit

# "Continuing Self" can be visible with dots

DotHabit fills the dots as you achieve your habits.
By doing this, you can have a sense of achievement at a glance and encouraged to continue.

# Add records and feel the results

It is hard to notice one's change. Because it is difficult to compare with oneself.
However, if you can compare it with yourself in the past, you will be able to notice your growth.
In DotHabit, you can have a record of your habits in writing.

creator: Shuto Yada
descriptionHtml:
Great lives start with great habits.

Imagine improving every day through positive habits and building a life you love. Start this journey with DotHabit!

DotHabit visualizes your daily habits with simple dots, providing instant satisfaction and encouraging persistence.

*********************
Key Features of DotHabit
*********************

# Visualize Consistency with Dots
Each time you fulfill a habit, DotHabit fills in a dot. This simple act allows you to see your achievements at a glance, spurring you on to continue.

# Record and Feel Your Progress
It's often hard to recognize personal growth because it's difficult to compare changes. With DotHabit, you can log your habits in writing and easily compare your progress with previous days, weeks, or even years, helping you notice your development over time.

# Notifications
Never forget a habit with our reminders. Watch your streaks grow and feel the sense of accomplishment that comes with it. The more you see your progress, the more motivated you'll be to maintain your great habits.

# Additional Features
- Choose from various theme colors.
- Enjoy a clean and simple design.
- Completely free.
etc.

*********************
In Conclusion
*********************

We look forward to your feedback and suggestions through the app. We review every comment to improve your experience.

Thank you for choosing DotHabit!

Privacy Policy: https://www.shutoo.jp/privacy/
Terms of Use: https://www.shutoo.jp/terms/

descriptionHtml:
Build Better Habits & Stay Motivated with Dots!

Great lives start with great habits. DotHabit helps you track daily habits, stay consistent, and build the life you want.

Join thousands of users improving their lives with this simple and powerful habit tracker.

*********************
Key Features of DotHabit
*********************

# Track Habits with Visual Dots
Each time you complete a habit, DotHabit fills in a dot. This provides instant satisfaction and a clear visual of your progress.

# Stay Motivated with Streaks
Watch your habit streaks grow and stay inspired to keep going.

# Smart Habit Reminders
Never miss a habit again. Set customizable reminders to build consistency.

# Log & Reflect on Your Journey
Write notes, review past habits, and track your growth over time.

# Personalized Experience
Customize themes, keep it simple, and stay focused on your self-improvement.

*********************
Who Is DotHabit For?
*********************

DotHabit is perfect for self-improvement enthusiasts, productivity seekers, and goal-driven individuals looking to:

- Develop stronger daily habits
- Improve self-care routines
- Stay consistent with fitness and gym goals
- Build mindfulness and reduce stress
- Track personal and professional growth

If you’re looking for a simple yet powerful daily planner, self-care tracker, and goal-setting tool, DotHabit is the perfect app to help you stay on track.

*********************
Get Started Today!
*********************

Start your habit-building journey today and watch your small wins add up to big changes.

Download DotHabit and make habit tracking effortless.
